dashboard_elements.body_text:
Filter - Date Range: Input the date range you want to view results for. Results are currently available for the last completed 24 months.
Filter - URL: Input the page URL or URLs if you want to view results for a specific page or pages. A reminder to input the various potential URL spellings. For example, include and not include the "www"; include and not include the "/" at the end of the URL; etc.
View or Download More Rows of Data: To view or download more rows of data, use the "Advanced data options" of the "Download Data" option. Go to the online guide for instructions.
